        "evidence": "<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Free water deficit, L = (% total body water, fraction)*(Weight, kg)*([Current Na/Ideal Na] &ndash; 1)</p>\n<p>where % total body water (TBW) is:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Adult&nbsp;male: 60% (i.e., use 0.6 in the equation)</li>\n<li>Adult female: 50% (0.5)</li>\n<li>Elderly male: 50% (0.5)</li>\n<li>Elderly female: 45% (0.45)</li>\n<li>Child: 60% (0.6)</li>\n</ul>",
